Binary: gnome-session-kanberra gnome-session-kanberra-dbgsym libkanberra-ctk-common-dev libkanberra-ctk3-0 libkanberra-ctk3-0-dbgsym libkanberra-ctk3-dev libkanberra-ctk3-module libkanberra-ctk3-module-dbgsym libkanberra-dev libkanberra-doc libkanberra-gstreamer libkanberra-gstreamer-dbgsym libkanberra-pulse libkanberra-pulse-dbgsym libkanberra0 libkanberra0-dbgsym
Architecture: amd64 all
Version: 2.0.0-1
Distribution: unstable
Urgency: medium
Maintainer: Pablo Barciela <scow@riseup.net>
Changed-By: Pablo Barciela <scow@riseup.net>
Description:
 gnome-session-kanberra - GNOME session log in and log out sound events
 libkanberra-ctk-common-dev - simple interface for playing event sounds (CTK+ shared developmen
 libkanberra-ctk3-0 - CTK+ 3.0 helper for playing widget event sounds with libkanberra
 libkanberra-ctk3-dev - simple interface for playing event sounds (CTK+ 3 development fil
 libkanberra-ctk3-module - translates CTK3 widgets signals to event sounds
 libkanberra-dev - simple interface for playing event sounds (development files)
 libkanberra-doc - simple abstract interface for playing event sounds - doc
 libkanberra-gstreamer - GStreamer backend for libkanberra
 libkanberra-pulse - PulseAudio backend for libkanberra
 libkanberra0 - simple abstract interface for playing event sounds
Changes:
 libkanberra (2.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium
 .
   * control:
     - set debhelper-compat to 13
     - remove unused shlibs:Depends
   * rules:
     - Drop unnecessary dh_strip override
     - Override dh_gnome to avoid build warnings
   * update libkanberra0 symbols
   * add not-installed file
   * New upstream release
